  <rte>
    <name>St. Sunday Crag and Helvellyn from Glenridding</name>
    <desc>This walk is demanding and involves a considerable amount of uphill walking but the rewards are ample with St Sunday Crag, Fairfield and the other summits all worthy of an ascent in their own right.</desc>
